<title>演得太好了，都没认出来！</title>
<link>http://www.jintiankansha.me/t/ujJP2S2cLb</link>
<guid isPermaLink="true" >http://www.jintiankansha.me/t/ujJP2S2cLb</guid>
<description>&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;当年看《绣春刀》里，阴恻恻的魏忠贤初一露面，跟张震扮的沈炼对戏，生死之际，话语高低起伏，笑声飘忽，跟烛影一样叵测。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;稍后跟聂远对戏时，情绪稳健些了，谈吐便换了风格，稳健流畅，几无起伏，大局尽在掌中。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;那时我稍微一愣神，“这语调，耳熟！”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;看演员表：噢，&lt;strong&gt;金士杰&lt;/strong&gt;先生啊！&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img data-ratio=&quot;0.6660617059891107&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/ichVicSguPRLnjNKqJLojVDyZT5oNAHiazcnibpJvK3q8d1uiboHoibkwvL7bwYIH5uSBPqAias5PTr0k5feBn4XcicibsA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;551&quot;/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;为什么要反应一下呢？&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;因为我之前老觉得，金士杰先生就该是《贞观之治》里，那个端正刚直，近于迂腐、侃侃而谈的魏征。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;所以认不出来，不只是魏征和魏忠贤气质不同，连说话方式都不同。金士杰的魏忠贤，那就是声音沙哑，高低起伏，阴恻恻冷笑，节奏忽快忽慢；魏征，那就是一本正经，字句平正。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;根本就是两个人。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;是所谓演技。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.6239316239316239&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ichVicSguPRLmia7grwyFWVKibuCLiciaVPNVok1h54ibKg2ibl6o8kAjZax0YxOTXDa2JLRWZlDdF7ribWEGHbxGarPlZg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;468&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;——金士杰先生曾经的好搭档&lt;strong&gt;李立群，&lt;/strong&gt;也演过魏忠贤，但那就容易辨别多了。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;《新龙门客栈》电视剧里，魏忠贤说话轻描淡写，威而不重，暗藏机锋，好听；可是李立群声音太易认，而且到哪部片子里，都是如此厚重。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;金士杰就藏得深些，一如他俩说相声，金士杰是那个故作笨拙的、接话的、总是恍然大悟的，捧哏。话不多，藏在暗影里，你都认不出他来。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;当然，李立群也能从阴险邪恶的魏忠贤随意转换到儒雅随和的田教授，不露痕迹。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;1993版《倚天屠龙记》里，他还演过朱元璋。那是我见过最好的朱元璋，让小时候的我觉得，“张无忌斗不过他，真不奇怪。”&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img data-ratio=&quot;0.7489539748953975&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/ichVicSguPRLnjNKqJLojVDyZT5oNAHiazcC7lUs1MRH7DP6PZuwRn6pCSkCTVibtkmH9ia5oicuWlKwSNpYv5OIAmQg/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;239&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img data-ratio=&quot;0.6646525679758308&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/ichVicSguPRLnjNKqJLojVDyZT5oNAHiazcvnJTWYYQxZBotnuvTo5wicUCicuicjkXicTSbHDBOVzaDgRle54lHUH5qA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;331&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;hr/&gt;
&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;有些角色，就是需要你认得出来。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;比如，&lt;strong&gt;姜文&lt;/strong&gt;如果缺了他独一无二的气派，《让子弹飞》整个的犷悍之气都会消弭。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;陈道明&lt;/strong&gt;在《唐山大地震》里如果不表现出他中年之后日益带有个人色彩的英锐之气，而是使《围城》里方鸿渐的儒雅气，他打陆毅的角色那一耳光，就无法让观众解气。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;这就像1990年代，香港所有导演都会让周润发朝小马哥和赌神方向走，露出那带杀气的笑脸——观众是为了这点才肯买票的。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;这几位是腕儿，是角儿，是谭鑫培《定军山》里舞花刀不掀背旗的独门绝技，是海报上的那张脸。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;电影观众在这方面，有种奇怪的执拗：他们既希望看到好演技，又希望看到自己心爱角色的招牌面孔——这两者有时，简直是矛盾的。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;hr/&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;但还是有另一种人的：他们演得好，演得太好，好得有时认不出来。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;比如，&lt;strong&gt;魏宗万老师&lt;/strong&gt;。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;我是看过了他的司马懿，后来也熟悉他的高俅。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;可是后来《三毛从军记》的老鬼，《孝子贤孙伺候着》的舅舅，我第一眼看，没认出来。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;后来《投名状》，我是为了看他和王奎荣老师，才看完的。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img data-ratio=&quot;0.6666666666666666&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/ichVicSguPRLnjNKqJLojVDyZT5oNAHiazcBDC0xlyVR815EroHfaEJ9IUWiaJV4ZjrvBIVIFJ0ia3bicuQhczL26x2w/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;300&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img data-ratio=&quot;0.6966666666666667&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/ichVicSguPRLnjNKqJLojVDyZT5oNAHiazcTJqDbekGicbTciaXun4zmibZc0IS9rOKtWpibWaHla0R9F0sIRRMlwXMZQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;600&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;比如，&lt;strong&gt;吕中&lt;/strong&gt;老师。她老人家演的《走向共和》慈禧，尽人皆知。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;但我得提醒一句，1987版《红楼梦》里老太君，是她配的音——我根本没意识到。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;比如，&lt;strong&gt;李明启&lt;/strong&gt;老师。她老人家的容嬷嬷不提了，但《我爱我家》里的李大妈、《水浒》里的王婆，《家有九凤》里的那位，真是各不相同。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img data-ratio=&quot;0.65&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/ichVicSguPRLnjNKqJLojVDyZT5oNAHiazcnAGpKamyAPzwXIicbzKu8mWjkKVtFs0pnsfadhHcoqBpBL4YU9C3hDw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img data-ratio=&quot;0.6644295302013423&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/ichVicSguPRLnjNKqJLojVDyZT5oNAHiazcvWZeTC1GO55JibQ96FC4p5n8YKaHDeu4ucriaOhcm4z84G5GeO8NZcEQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;596&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

